is no error handling, there is no support for <span class=\"RktSym\"><a class=\"RktValLink Sq\" data-pltdoc=\"x\" href=\"https://docs.racket-lang.org/reference/values.html#%28def._%28%28quote._~23~25kernel%29._values%29%29\">values</a></span>, and many more subtle things the real promise library handles. Regardless,\nthis provides insights into the inner workings of the library and an interesting algorithm for collapsing indirection.</p>"))))